Name
       viewLast - Displays the last view window or the previous view

Syntax
       viewLast [-help]

       Displays  the  last view window or the previous view. This command pro-
       vides the same function as the Zoom Previous icon (bindkey w).

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the viewLast command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man viewLast.

